\c 17
\s Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lifika kuElija umprofethi
\p
\v 1 UElija umTishibi wabahlali beGileyadi wasesithi kuAhabi: Kuphila kukaJehova, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 17.12. 18.10,15. 22.14. 2 Kho. 3.14. 5.16. Ruthe 3.13.\x*, engimi phambi kwakhe\x + 18.15. Dute. 10.8.\x*, kakuyikuba khona lamazolo lezulu\x + Jak. 5.17.\x* kuliminyaka, kuphela njengokwelizwi lami\x + 18.1.\x*.
\v 2 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuye lisithi:
\v 3 Suka lapha, wena uphendukele empumalanga, uzicatshise esifuleni iKerithi, esiphambi kweJordani.
\v 4 Kuzakuthi-ke unathe esifuleni; sengilaye amawabayi ukuthi akondle khona.
\v 5 Wasehamba wenza njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba wayahlala esifuleni iKerithi esiphambi kweJordani.
\v 6 Amawabayi asemlethela isinkwa lenyama ekuseni, lesinkwa lenyama ntambama; wanatha esifuleni.
\v 7 Kwasekusithi emva kwesikhathi isifula satsha, ngoba kwakungelazulu elizweni.
\s UElija lomfelokazi weZarefathi
\p
\v 8 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuye lisithi:
\v 9 Sukuma uye eZarefathi engeyeSidoni, uhlale khona\x + Obad. 1.20.\x*. Khangela, ngilayile owesifazana ongumfelokazi khona ukuthi akondle.
\v 10 Wasukuma-ke waya eZarefathi\x + Obad. 1.20.\x*. Lapho efika esangweni lomuzi, khangela, owesifazana ongumfelokazi wayelapho etheza inkuni\x + Nani 15.32,33.\x*; wasembiza wathi: Ake ungikhele amanzi amalutshwana ngenkezo ukuze nginathe.
\v 11 Kwathi esahamba ukuya\add wa\add*thatha, wambiza wathi: Ake ungiphathele ucezu lwesinkwa esandleni sakho.
\v 12 Wasesithi: Kuphila kukaJehova uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 17.12. 18.10,15. 22.14. 2 Kho. 3.14. 5.16. Ruthe 3.13.\x*, kangilaqebelengwana, kuphela impuphu egcwala isandla embizeni lamafutha ayingcosana esiphisweni; khangela-ke ngitheza\x + Nani 15.32,33.\x* izinkuni ezimbili ukuze ngingene ngizilungisele khona mina lendodana yami, ukuze sidle sife\x + Isa. 17.6. Jer. 3.14.\x*.
\v 13 UElija wasesithi kuye: Ungesabi; hamba wenze njengokwelizwi lakho, kodwa ngenzela kuqala iqebelengwana elincinyane ngakho, u\add li\add*lethe lapha kimi, ngemva kwalokho-ke wenzele wena lendodana yakho.
\v 14 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakoIsrayeli: Imbiza yempuphu kayiyikuphela, lesiphiso samafutha kasiyikuswela, kuze kube lusuku iN\nd kosi\nd* ezanisa ngalo izulu ebusweni bomhlaba.
\v 15 Wasehamba wenza njengokwelizwi likaElija. Njalo yena \add kanye\add* laye lendlu yakhe badla okwensuku \add ezinengi\add*.
\v 16 Imbiza yempuphu kayiphelanga lesiphiso samafutha kasiswelanga, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* eyalikhuluma ngesandla sikaElija.
\p
\v 17 Kwasekusithi emva kwalezizinto, indodana yowesifazana, inkosikazi yendlu, yagula; lomkhuhlane wayo wawulamandla kangangokuthi akwaze kwasala umphefumulo kuyo.
\v 18 Wasesithi kuElija: Ngilani lawe\x + 2 Sam. 16.10. Luka 5.8.\x*, muntu kaNkulunkulu\x + Hlu. 13.6.\x*? Uze kimi ukuze kukhumbuleke isono sami lokubulala indodana yami na\x + Nani 5.15.\x*?
\v 19 Wasesithi kuye: Nginika indodana yakho. Waseyithatha esifubeni sakhe, wayenyusela endlini ephezulu lapho ayehlala khona, wayilalisa embhedeni wakhe\x + 17.23.\x*.
\v 20 Wasekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni wathi: N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wami, umehlisele ububi lalo umfelokazi engingenise kwakhe ngokubulala indodana yakhe na\x + 2 Kho. 4.33-35.\x*?
\v 21 Wasezelulela phezu komntwana kathathu, wakhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni wathi: N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu wami, ake ubuyele umphefumulo walumntwana phakathi kwakhe\x + 2 Kho. 4.33-35.\x*.
\v 22 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasilizwa ilizwi likaElija, umphefumulo womntwana wasubuyela phakathi kwakhe, wasebuya ephila\x + Heb. 11.35.\x*.
\v 23 UElija wasemthatha umntwana, wamehlisa esuka endlini ephezulu waya endlini, wamnika unina; uElija wasesithi: Bona, indodana yakho iyaphila\x + 17.23.\x*.
\v 24 Owesifazana wasesithi kuElija: Khathesi sengisazi\x + Joha. 3.2; 16.30.\x* lokhu, ukuthi ungumuntu kaNkulunkulu, ukuthi ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* elisemlonyeni wakho liliqiniso\x + Hlu. 13.6.\x*.